# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .env.local — React Dashboard Environment Variables
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# SETUP:
#   1. Copy this file to .env.local:  cp .env.local.example .env.local
#   2. Get credentials from: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/YOUR_PROJECT/settings/api
#   3. Fill in your Supabase URL and anon key below
#
# ⚠️  NOTE: .env.local is in .gitignore and will NOT be committed
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Supabase Configuration
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# INSTRUCTIONS:
#
# 1. Go to your Supabase project dashboard
# 2. Navigate to Settings → API
# 3. Copy "Project URL" and paste as VITE_SUPABASE_URL
# 4. Copy "Project API keys → anon public" and paste as VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#
# Example values (replace with your actual values):
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://abcdefghijklmno.supabase.co
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
